    earlier work or a work "based on" the earlier work.
  
  (1.3) A "covered work" means either the unmodified Program or a work based
    on the Program.
  
  (1.4) "Executable Form" means any form of the work other than Source Code Form.
  
  (1.5) "Source Code Form" means the form of the work preferred for making modifications.
  
  (1.6) "You" (or "Your")
    means an individual or a legal entity exercising rights under this
